0.3 (2016-11-21):

  * Experimental support for Caja and Nemo
  * Fix resolving path to virtual (desktop shortcut) locations
  * Add support for pausing operations
  * Add progress text
  * Report operations' non-fatal warnings
  * Add more meaningful titles to the dialogs
  * Update translations: de, fr
  * New help translations: fr


0.2.1 (2014-01-23):

  Minor maintenance release.

  * Build system fixes
  * No functional changes


0.2 (2013-05-28):

  Minor improvements release with major code changes.

  * Code refactoring and cleanup
  * Build for Nautilus 3.x by default
  * Drop GConf dependency for Nautilus 3.x
  * New translations: de, ru


0.1.1 (2011-08-18):

  Minor improvements of 0.1 release.

  * Support for GTK 3.x (and thus Nautilus 3.x)
  * Minor UI cleanup of the progress dialog


0.1 (2011-05-15):

  Initial release.
